      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm like 3 days ago. i've been taking them every day but honestly the redness and the swelling are basically totally gone now and i feel fine. do i really need to keep taking them for the full 10 days if the infection is already gone? i dont really want to keep putting stuff in my system if i dont have to.",
